sections.heading: to 509.385 are operative
sections.text:
and in full force and effect. A written statement of the Attorney General of

the State of Oregon, dated October 16, 1957, states that the provisions of

509.360 are satisfied.

sections.heading: to 509.590 and 509.595
sections.text:

a part of ORS chapter 509 or any series therein by legislative action. See

Preface to Oregon Revised Statutes for further explanation.
